subject: College Athletics
Football
lead_paragraph: Versus will televise 23 college football games this season, up from 19 last season, including five Ivy League games. Versus will also televise eight games from the Mountain West Conference and five each from the Pac-10 and Big 12. Among the Ivy League games Versus is scheduled to televise is the 125th Harvard-Yale game.
